== ft.easy_language_select.php

Language dropdown for ExpressionEngine using FieldFrame.

== Usage

When setting up the field, you can choose whether it should be translated into the native language (if possible)

To display the name of the language in your field: {fieldname}

To display the language code: {fieldname code="yes"}

== Current Version

1.0 (6 July 2010)

== Requirements

FieldFrame

